@startuml
title Agent Session Status Lifecycle

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Discovered : session file or rollout found
Discovered --> Unknown : recent file without live process
Discovered --> Waiting : live process is idle
Discovered --> Thinking : user message has no assistant reply yet
Discovered --> Executing : open tool call or active child process

Waiting --> UserInput : no explicit decision request
Waiting --> UserDecision : approval, confirmation,\nor choice is pending
UserInput --> Thinking : user sends a new prompt
UserDecision --> Thinking : user confirms or chooses

Thinking --> Executing : assistant starts a tool call
Thinking --> Waiting : assistant reply completed
Executing --> Thinking : tool result returned
Executing --> Waiting : tool finished and no generation is active

Waiting --> RateLimited : quota is exhausted and reset is in the future
RateLimited --> Waiting : quota reset time passes

Executing --> Done : exec session completed
Thinking --> Done : task_complete event
Waiting --> Done : owning process exits
Unknown --> [*]
Done --> [*]
@enduml
